### Burpsuite and Packet Injection

Of all the tools in a hacker's aresenal, Burpsuite is a very unique one. It is packed full of features for website penetration testing. 
Burpsuite's primary use is to intercept packet requests sent to a server. 

### HTTP and HTTPS

When you go on the internet, and look at your URL of whatever page you are on, you might have noticed that at the beginning of it there is http:// or https://.
This references the Hyper Text Transfer Protocol and the Secure version of it. HTTP is not encrypted, whereas HTTPS is encrypted. 

